Description: Shadowfetch branding assets
 Ships the Shadowfetch ASCII logo (consumed by fastfetch), the
 message-of-the-day, a versioned os-release source consumed by
 the live-build chroot hook during ISO assembly, and miscellaneous
 brand-identity files.
